      "widgets_values": [
        "[Tutorial](https://github.com/wildminder/ComfyUI-Kandinsky\n)\n\n**put the models in a folder named kandinsky in the diffusion_models folder**\n\n| Model                               | Config Name              | Duration | Hugging Face Link |\n|:------------------------------------|:-------------------------|:--------:|:------------------|\n| Kandinsky SFT 5s       | `config_5s_sft.yaml`     | 5s       |🤗 [HF](https://huggingface.co/kandinskylab/Kandinsky-5.0-T2V-Lite-sft-5s/resolve/main/model/kandinsky5lite_t2v_sft_5s.safetensors) |\n| Kandinsky SFT 10s      | `config_10s_sft.yaml`    | 10s      |🤗 [HF](https://huggingface.co/kandinskylab/Kandinsky-5.0-T2V-Lite-sft-10s/resolve/main/model/kandinsky5lite_t2v_sft_10s.safetensors) |\n| Kandinsky pretrain 5s  | `config_5s_pretrain.yaml`| 5s       |🤗 [HF](https://huggingface.co/kandinskylab/Kandinsky-5.0-T2V-Lite-pretrain-5s/resolve/main/model/kandinsky5lite_t2v_pretrain_5s.safetensors) |\n| Kandinsky pretrain 10s | `config_10s_pretrain.yaml`| 10s      |🤗 [HF](https://huggingface.co/kandinskylab/Kandinsky-5.0-T2V-Lite-pretrain-10s/resolve/main/model/kandinsky5lite_t2v_pretrain_10s.safetensors) |\n| Kandinsky no-CFG 5s    | `config_5s_nocfg.yaml`   | 5s       |🤗 [HF](https://huggingface.co/kandinskylab/Kandinsky-5.0-T2V-Lite-nocfg-5s/resolve/main/model/kandinsky5lite_t2v_nocfg_5s.safetensors) |\n| Kandinsky no-CFG 10s   | `config_10s_nocfg.yaml`  | 10s      |🤗 [HF](https://huggingface.co/kandinskylab/Kandinsky-5.0-T2V-Lite-nocfg-10s/resolve/main/model/kandinsky5lite_t2v_nocfg_10s.safetensors) |\n| Kandinsky distill 5s   | `config_5s_distil.yaml`  | 5s       |🤗 [HF](https://huggingface.co/kandinskylab/Kandinsky-5.0-T2V-Lite-distilled16steps-5s/resolve/main/model/kandinsky5lite_t2v_distilled16steps_5s.safetensors) |\n| Kandinsky distill 10s  | `config_10s_distil.yaml` | 10s      |🤗 [HF](https://huggingface.co/kandinskylab/Kandinsky-5.0-T2V-Pro-sft-5s/resolve/main/model/kandinsky5pro_t2v_sft_5s.safetensors) |\n| Kandinsky t2v pro 5s  | `config_5s_t2v_pro_20b.yaml` | 5s      |🤗 [HF](https://huggingface.co/kandinskylab/Kandinsky-5.0-T2V-Lite-distilled16steps-10s/resolve/main/model/kandinsky5lite_t2v_distilled16steps_10s.safetensors) |\n| Kandinsky i2v 5s  | `config_5s_sft.yaml` | 5s      |🤗 [HF](https://huggingface.co/ai-forever/Kandinsky-5.0-I2V-Lite-5s/resolve/main/model/kandinsky5lite_i2v_5s.safetensors) |\n\nYou can also use [ggufs](https://huggingface.co/Ada321/Kandinsky-5.0-T2V-Pro-sft-5s-Q4_K_S.gguf/resolve/main/kandinsky5Pro_t2v_sft_5s-Q4_K_S.gguf) or pre-quanted fp8_scaled, just select them. For fp8 on_the_fly quants the full model into fp8, with_map used a pre-quanted weights if you select them and have a matching _scales.pt file.\n\n\n**VAE**\n- [hunyuan_video_vae_bf16.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/HunyuanVideo_repackaged/resolve/main/split_files/vae/hunyuan_video_vae_bf16.safetensors)\n\n**Text Encoder**   \n- [clip-vit-large-patch14](https://huggingface.co/openai/clip-vit-large-patch14/resolve/main/model.safetensors)\n- [qwen_2.5_vl_7b_fp8_scaled.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/qwen_2.5_vl_7b_fp8_scaled.safetensors)\nFile save location\n\n```\nComfyUI/\n├───📂 models/\n│   ├───📂 diffusion_models/\n│   │   └─── 📂 kandinsky/\n│   │         └───kandinsky_whatever.safetensors\n│   ├───📂 text_encoders/\n│   │   ├─── clip-vit-large-patch14\n│   │   └─── qwen_2.5_vl_7b_fp8_scaled.safetensors \n│   └───📂 vae/\n│       └── hunyuan_vae.safetensors\n```"
